Code preview of the table SYS_菜单

drop table "SYS_Menu" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_Menu" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_Menu"
(
"MenuID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"MenuCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"MenuName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"Level" INTEGER not null,
"ParentID" NUMBER(10),
"ActionURL" NVARCHAR2(200),
"OrderNum" NUMBER(10) not null,
"Type" INTEGER not null,
"Icon" VARCHAR2(100),
"IsDisplay" INTEGER not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"OnlyforiPad" INTEGER default 0,
constraint PK_SYS_MENU primary key ("MenuID")
);

comment on column "SYS_Menu"."Level" is
'0，1，2共3级';

comment on column "SYS_Menu"."Type" is
'1: 可视化菜单
2：原REM菜单';

comment on column "SYS_Menu"."IsDisplay" is
'1: 启用
0: 停用';

comment on column "SYS_Menu"."Enable" is
'1: 启用
0: 停用';
